### Get all contacts
GET http://localhost:3000/contacts

### Get single contact
GET http://localhost:3000/contacts/:contactId

### Create new contact
POST http://localhost:3000/contacts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Luke",
  "lastName": "Skywalker",
  "email": "luke.skywalker@jedi.com",
  "favoriteColor": "green",
  "birthday": "1977-05-25"
}

### Update contact
PUT http://localhost:3000/contacts/:contactId
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Darth",
  "lastName": "Vader",
  "email": "darth.vader@sith.com",
  "favoriteColor": "red",
  "birthday": "1977-05-25"
}

### Delete contact
DELETE http://localhost:3000/contacts/:contactId